/33aa59de8765e5b6b709587063e915ba.mp4?t=1748943924\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >To be kept up to date on all things <strong>Deepest Chamber: Resurrection</strong>, make sure to join <strong>our dedicated Discord server</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552080/extras/0068e5b0b8055b27749cf92b2ff611a7.poster.avif?t=1748943924\" width=600 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1552080/extras/0068e5b0b8055b27749cf92b2ff611a7.webm?t=1748943924\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
